        "en": {
          "commentary": "The 2026 wireless gaming mouse market has reached a performance plateau at the top tier, with multiple options offering sub-1ms wireless latency and class-leading sensors. Logitech's G Pro X Superlight 2 DEX remains the esports community's consensus #1 choice, combining the HERO 2 sensor's flawless tracking with an asymmetric shape preferred by most FPS players. Razer's DeathAdder V3 HyperSpeed surged to #2 by delivering the beloved ergonomic shape at only 64g with excellent value at $99. The Endgame Gear OP1we stands out at #3 for weight-obsessed users at just 55g. Notable: the Corsair M75 Air climbs to #5 with its 60g frame and Slipstream wireless, displacing the previously popular Fnatic Bolt.",
